These exact values must not change (tests assert them):

| Concern | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Error messages | Must match verbatim: `"Product not found"`, `"Order not found"`, `"adjustment must be a number"`, `"Insufficient stock"`, `"userId and items are required"`, `"Order must have at least one item"`, `"Quantity must be positive"`, `"Invalid status. Must be one of: …"`, `"Cannot transition from X to Y"` |
